{"id": "art-189", "label": "Art. 189", "title": "Art. 189", "slug": "art-189", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 189 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='color:black'>(1)În\nsocietatea în comandit&#259; pe <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span>,\nadministratorii vor putea fi <span class=SpellE>revoca&#355;i</span> de\nadunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;ionarilor</span>, printr-o\nhot&#259;râre luat&#259; cu majoritatea stabilit&#259; pentru adun&#259;rile\nextraordinare.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_412634620\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1969\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_412634620\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Adunarea general&#259;, cu <span class=SpellE>aceea&#351;i</span>\nmajoritate, alege alt&#259; persoan&#259; în locul administratorului revocat,\ndecedat sau care a încetat exercitarea mandatului s&#259;u.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)Numirea trebuie aprobat&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de <span class=SpellE>ceilal&#355;i</span>\nadministratori, dac&#259; sunt mai <span class=SpellE>mul&#355;i</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(4)Noul administrator devine asociat\ncomanditat.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(5)Administratorul revocat\nr&#259;mâne r&#259;spunz&#259;tor nelimitat <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde <span class=SpellE>ter&#355;i</span> pentru <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span>\npe care le-a contractat în timpul <span class=SpellE>administra&#355;iei</span>\nsale, putând îns&#259; exercita <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iune</span> în\nregres împotriva <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>"}